>
  <section class="hero">
    <span class="hero-tag">Updated March 2026</span>
    <h1>Ghana Business Intelligence That Tells You What Actually Fails</h1>
    <p>Every consultant says Ghana is amazing. We tell you where the money goes to die — and where it actually survives. Evidence-grounded analysis for diaspora founders and investors.</p>
