        <h3>Cocoa Crisis: Cocobod Debt and What It Means for Agri-Investment</h3>
        <p>Cocobod's debt restructuring creates both risk and opportunity in Ghana's cocoa sector. Here's the honest assessment for investors considering agri-processing.</p>
